# Trunk vs GitFlow (lab summary)

| Criteria | Git Flow | Trunk |
| -------- | -------- | ----- |
| Main branches | main + develop | main |
| Feature LT | days-weeks | hours-1-2days |
| Release | release/* branches | tag on main |
| DevOps IaC | unusual | often |
| Hooks | pre-commit secrets | same | 

Recomendation: trunk + PR + CI on main.
